page.title: 05TRANSPORT SURVEY,WATERLANE.
page.content:
The majority of people in the Waterlane area own{cars}aged from 1978 -1985.The most popular make of car is {Ford.}Many of the people in Waterlane like bright coloured vehicles.The majority of people go to work in cars. Excluding holidays people travel about {50m a day.}People normally get their petrol from Bisley garage which is the nearest garage to them.4 out of 5 people's cars are{hatchback.}Most people have 1 or more cars(these cars are usually housed in garages.)People also have other vehicles like motorbikes,mopeds and push bikes.There is{no public transport.}
